<doc id="219795" wikidata="Q231619" url="?curid=219795" title="Stern (disambiguation)">
<text>The [[stern]] is the rear or aft part of a ship or boat.

Stern may also refer to:

==People==
* Stern (given name)
* Stern (surname)
* Stern family, a Jewish French banking family
* Daniel Stern, pen name of Marie d&#x27;Agoult (1805–1876), author and paramour of Franz Liszt

