* 2002: Michael Foss, &quot;Out of India: A Raj Childhood&quot;
* 2003: Jenny Diski, &quot;Stranger on a Train&quot;
* 2004: Bryan Magee, &quot;Clouds of Glory: A Hoxton Childhood&quot;
